      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "Evidence for the role of acetate in fatty-acid biosynthesis comes from isotope-labeling experiments. If acetate labeled with <sup>13</sup>C in the methyl group (<sup>13</sup>CH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>2</sub>H) were incorporated into fatty acids, at what positions in the fatty-acid chain would you expect the <sup>13</sup>C label to appear?",
